data.description: This highly desirable 4-bedroom, 2-1/2 bath Nalu model has it all.  ENERGY SAVING - low-E dual paned vinyl windows, central a/c, solar water heating system, LED lighting package, programmable smart thermostat. Owners have installed 10 OWNED PV panels & a Tesla battery storage unit.  INTERIOR - 9' ceilings in living room areas, upgraded laminate floors in 1st floor living area and kitchen, wall to wall carpet upstairs, Corian kitchen countertops, Kohler plumbing fixtures, ceiling lights in all bedrooms, USB outlets in bedrooms & kitchen, owner added LED nightlights, security system, all Bosch kitchen appliances except for GE refrigerator, upgraded GE washer/dryer and much, much more. EXTERIOR - composite roof with limited lifetime warranty, James Hardi siding with 30-year limited warranty, common area front yard landscaping.   Cleaned and move-in ready!  Seabridge...a place to call home.
